wiki.summary: “Light Switch” was released January 20, 2022 as the lead single for Charlie Puth's self-titled third studio album. In a Vogue interview, he calls this body of work "his most personal". Also during the interview, he confirmed his album would be released later in the year 2022. Read more on Last.fm.
